partman-reiserfs (12) unstable; urgency=low

  * Colin Watson
    - Depend on partman.
  * Anton Zinoviev
    - send output of modprobe to /dev/null.
    - remove a comma from the German translation of the notail part of
      partman-reiserfs/options.  Thanks to Alexander Lazarevic, 
      closes: #238689. 
    - commit.d/format_reiserfs: do not use timestamps of the form
      "formatted_as_reiserfs", but use just "formatted".  This allows
      other parts of partma to know whether some partition is going to be
      formatted again or not. 
    - remove dependency on partman as otherwise main-menu falls in
      infinite loop - partman depends on partman-target, partman-target
      depends on partman-basicfilesystems

  * Updated translations: 
    - Bulgarian (bg.po) by Ognyan Kulev
    - German (de.po) by Dennis Stampfer
    - Spanish (Castilian) (es.po) by Javier Fernandez-Sanguino Peña
    - Norwegian Nynorsk (nn.po) by Håvard Korsvoll
    - Swedish (sv.po) by André Dahlqvist
  
 -- Anton Zinoviev <zinoviev@debian.org>  Sat, 15 May 2004 07:42:21 +0300

